# Force LF line endings for every text file in the repo, on every
# platform. Without this, git on Windows applies core.autocrlf=true
# during checkout, rewrites text files to CRLF, and prettier --check
# then fails the CI lint job on windows-latest.
#
# * text=auto tells git this is a text file and normalize on checkin.
# eol=lf pins the working-tree line ending to LF regardless of the
# host's core.autocrlf setting.
*                text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files that must not be touched.
*.wasm           binary
*.png            binary
*.jpg            binary
*.jpeg           binary
*.gif            binary
*.ico            binary
*.woff           binary
*.woff2          binary
